data.description: ** Seller Offering $5,000 Concession toward Buyers Closing Costs!**   All Brick Home with a fenced back yard and a beautiful open concept Living Room w/ Natural Gas Fireplace, Spacious Eat-in-Kitchen features Granite Tops, plenty of Cabinet Space & a Moveable Island! Large Primary Bedroom with a WIC. This home has a split layout with 3 rooms on the opposite side of the home the Primary Suite! Bonus Room above the Garage has a Half Bath & Attic Storage Space! True Laundry Room with plenty of storage. Double Vanity in Guest Bath w/ Separate Shower! New Refrigerator, Microwave, Stove and Dishwasher installed in June 2022 along with a Whole House Tankless Water Heater installed in July 2022.   Buyer and Buyers Agent to verify all information
